item.title: Prayer bpn9120 in Kalaallisut
item.description: Pilluaqqunneqarli manna, illu, sumiiffillu, illoqarfillu, uummallu, qaqqarlu, toqqorsimaffillu, qaarusullu, qoororlu, nunalu, imarlu, qeqertarlu, narsarlu, Guutimik eqqartuiffiusimasoq nersorneqaatissaanillu unnersiorfiusimasoq.
